32:41.336 --> 32:42.412
Anything.

32:43.445 --> 32:44.982
Can I marry you one day?

32:45.439 --> 32:46.709
(CHUCKLES)

32:47.394 --> 32:52.107
♪ <i>Everything all at once</i> ♪

